{"article_id":"v2JaMIJwsc3ROTRN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump has threatened severe sanctions against Iraq","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"after its parliament called on US troops to leave the country .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"`` We have a very extraordinarily expensive air base","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that 's there .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"It cost billions of dollars","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to build .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"We 're not leaving","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"unless they pay us back for it , ''","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"Tensions are high","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"after the US assassinated Iranian General Qasem Soleimani in Baghdad last week .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Soleimani , 62 , spearheaded Iranian military operations in the Middle East ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"and was regarded as a terrorist by the US .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The general 's remains have now returned to his home country ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"where mourners packed the streets of Tehran early on Monday .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"The new head of Iran 's Quds force","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"which Soleimani led -","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"has vowed to expel the US from the Middle East .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"`` We promise to continue martyr Soleimani 's path with the same force ...","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"and the only compensation for us would be to remove America from the region , ''","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"state radio quoted Esmail Qaani","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"as saying .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"The strike","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"that killed Soleimani","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"also claimed the life of Abu Mahdi al-Muhandis , a top Iraqi military figure","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"who commanded the Iranian-backed Kataib Hezbollah group .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Speaking from the presidential plane ,","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Mr Trump said","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"if Iraq asked US forces to depart on an unfriendly basis ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"`` we will charge them sanctions","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"like they 've never seen before , ever .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"It 'll make Iranian sanctions look somewhat tame . ''","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Some 5,000 US soldiers are in Iraq as part of the international coalition against the Islamic State","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"( IS )","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"group .","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"On Sunday , the coalition paused its operations against IS in Iraq ,","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"and Iraqi MPs passed a non-binding resolution","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"calling for foreign troops to leave .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"The resolution was pushed through by the parliament 's Shia Muslim bloc","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"which is close to Iran .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Iran has announced","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"it will no longer abide by restrictions","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"imposed by the 2015 nuclear deal ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"under which it agreed to limit its sensitive nuclear activities and allow in international inspectors in return for the lifting of economic sanctions .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"US President Donald Trump abandoned the deal in 2018 ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"he wanted to force Iran to negotiate a new deal","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that would place indefinite curbs on its nuclear programme","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and also halt its development of ballistic missiles .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Iran refused","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"and had since been gradually rolling back its commitments under the deal .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"In a statement , it said","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"it would no longer observe limitations on its capacity for enrichment , the level of enrichment , the stock of enriched material , or research and development .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"The leaders of Germany , France and the UK","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"- which were all signatories to the 2015 deal , alongside China and Russia -","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"responded with a joint statement","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"urging Iran to refrain from `` further violent action or proliferation '' .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"`` It is crucial now to de-escalate .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"We call on all the players involved to show utmost restraint and responsibility , ''","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"they said .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Mr Trump has vowed to strike back at Iran in the event of retaliation for Soleimani 's death , `` perhaps in a disproportionate manner '' .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"He also repeated a controversial threat","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"to target Iranian cultural sites on Sunday ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"despite criticism from within the US and overseas .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"`` They 're allowed to kill our people .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"They 're allowed to torture and maim our people .","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"They 're allowed to use roadside bombs","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"and blow up our people .","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"And we 're not allowed to touch their cultural site ?","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"It does n't work that way , ''","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"the president said .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"In a series of tweets on Saturday , Mr Trump said","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"the US had identified 52 Iranian sites , some `` at a very high level & important to Iran & the Iranian culture '' ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"and warned","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"they would be `` HIT VERY FAST AND HARD ''","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"if Tehran struck at the US .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"US Senator Elizabeth Warren , a senior member of the Democratic Party , responded","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"by tweeting :","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"`` You are threatening to commit war crimes . ''","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Iran 's Foreign Minister Mohammad Javad Zarif drew parallels with IS destruction of the Middle East 's cultural riches .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"`` A reminder to those","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"hallucinating about emulating ISIS war crimes","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"by targeting our cultural heritage , ''","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"`` Through MILLENNIA of history , barbarians have come","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"and ravaged our cities ,","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"razed our monuments","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"and burnt our libraries .","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"Where are they now ?","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"We 're still here ,","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"& standing tall . ''","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Targeting cultural sites is banned under the Geneva and Hague Conventions","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"- and violating them would constitute a war crime in the US .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"Iran is home to two dozen Unesco World Heritage sites .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"These are landmarks","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"the UN 's cultural organisation believes","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"need preserving for their cultural , historic or scientific significance .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"They include :","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Persepolis , the capital of the ancient Persian Achaemenid empire","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"and whose earliest remains date back to Sixth Century BC","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Naqsh-e Jahan Square in the city of Isfahan ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"which was built in the early 17th Century","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"and is is one of the largest city squares in the world","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Golestan Palace in Tehran , the residence and seat of power for the Qajar dynasty","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"which ruled Iran from 1785 to 1925","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"There are also a number of sites which","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"- while not listed by Unesco -","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"still retain huge cultural importance .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"For example , the Azadi","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"( Freedom )","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Tower in Tehran has been the gathering point for celebrations , military parades and mass demonstrations for almost 50 years .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"Elsewhere in the city , the Mausoleum of Ruhollah Khomeini is dedicated to the Islamic Republic 's founder","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"and also houses the tombs of some of the country 's leading political figures .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"The country has always insisted","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"that its nuclear programme is entirely peaceful -","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"but suspicions","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"that it was being used","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"to develop a bomb","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"covertly prompted the UN Security Council , US and EU to impose crippling sanctions in 2010 .","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"The 2015 deal was designed to constrain the programme in a verifiable way in return for sanctions relief .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"It restricted Iran 's enrichment of uranium ,","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"which is used","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"to make reactor fuel","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"but also nuclear weapons ,","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"to 3.67 % .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Iran was also required to redesign a heavy-water reactor","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"being built ,","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"whose spent fuel would contain plutonium suitable for a bomb ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"and allow international inspections .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Before July 2015 , Iran had a large stockpile of enriched uranium and almost 20,000 centrifuges , enough","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"to create eight to 10 bombs ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"according to the White House at the time .","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"US experts estimated back then","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"if Iran had decided to rush to make a bomb ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"it would take two to three months","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"until it had enough 90 % -enriched uranium","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"to build a nuclear weapon","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"- the so-called `` breakout time '' .","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"Iran 's current `` breakout time '' ,","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"should it attempt to build a nuclear bomb ,","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"is estimated to be around a year ,","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"but this could be reduced to half a year or even a matter of months","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"if enrichment levels are increased to 20 % , for example .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":293,"left":180,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":155,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":148,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":151,"right":152,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":149,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":168,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":160,"right":167,"relation":"context","nu